                      <para>
                        <text>in the case of a body corporate, to a fine not exceeding $100,000.</text>
                      </para>
                    </label-para>
                  </para>
                </subprov>
                <subprov quote="1" skeleton="no">
                  <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">4</label>
                  <para>
                    <text>To avoid doubt, in this section and <changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">sections 212 and 213</citation></changeable>, <def-term id="DLM1139645">tobacco</def-term> means all tobacco (as defined in section 2(1)), whether manufactured or not manufactured.</text>
                  </para>
